  <p>The pilot is successful if:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Teams can onboard successfully</li>
    <li>Backlog generation is useful</li>
    <li>Jira reflects engineering activity</li>
    <li>Teams complete a real use case</li>
    <li>Feedback helps refine the workflow</li>
  </ul>

